{
    "chapter": 54,
    "verses": {
        "1": {
            "verses": {
                "54:1": {
                    "id": 1
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>复活的时刻业已临近。在先知（愿主福安之）时期月亮曾破裂，月亮的破裂是先知（愿主福安之）的奇迹之一。</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "54:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以物配主者每当看到证实先知（愿主福安之）之真实的一项迹象时，他们便拒绝接受，而且说：“我们没有看到证据，这只是一种荒谬的魔术。”</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "54:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们否认来临他们的真理，而追随他们荒谬的私欲，所有事物——或善或恶——在复活日都将获得其应得的。</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "54:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>之前不信道的民众被真主毁灭的消息已经来临他们，这足以制止他们的不信道和不义。</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "54:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>来临他们的是完美的智慧，是对付他们的托辞。对于不信道否认复活之人警告是无效的。</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "54:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！如果他们不遵循正道，你就回避他们，等待掌管吹号角的天使，召唤众生经历他们全然不知的大事。</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "54:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们目视低下，从坟墓里出来，象乱飞的蝗虫一样奔向清算场，</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "54:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>极速奔向清算场的召唤者面前，不信道者说：“这天是灾难之日，其中有极为恐惧和严厉的刑罚。”</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "54:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>“在这些否认你号召之人之前，我派遣我的仆人奴哈（愿主赐其平安）劝化时，他的族人否认了他，还说奴哈是‘疯子’，如果他继续号召，他们就以谩骂和污言恐吓斥责他。</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "54:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>奴哈祈祷他的主说：“我的民众压迫了我，没有响应我，求你降下惩罚，使我战胜他们吧！”</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "54:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>故我就以连绵不断的骤雨打开天上诸多扇门，</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "54:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我破开大地，使其成为涌出水的泉眼，天上降下的水和地下冒出的水，依真主既定的安排而相会，故水淹没了一切，除真主欲拯救者外。</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "54:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我使奴哈乘上用木板和钉子制造的船舶，拯救了他及与他一道之人免遭淹溺。</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "54:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这艘船在我的眷顾和呵护下于波涛汹涌的水浪中行走，他们否认了奴哈带来的启示，这是对曾被族人否认的奴哈的援助。</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "54:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我使我给予他们的惩罚成为一种觉悟者的借鉴，有因此觉悟之人吗？</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "54:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我对否认者的惩罚怎样的？！我毁灭他们的警告是怎样的？！</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "54:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我确已使《古兰经》成为容易背诵和觉悟的，有因此觉悟和接受劝告之人吗？</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "54:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>阿德人否认了他们的先知胡德（愿主赐其平安）。麦加的人们啊！你们当想到我对他们的惩罚是怎样的？我以给予他们的惩罚成为对世人的警告。</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "54:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在一个凶恶不吉的日子里，我派遣冷酷的飓风惩罚了他们，</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "54:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>暴风把人从地上拔起，再将他们倒着扔出，他们就像是从土地里被拔起的椰枣树干一样。</p>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "54:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>麦加的人们啊！你们想想我对他们的惩罚是怎样的？我以给予他们的惩罚成为对世人的警告。</p>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "54:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我确已使《古兰经》成为容易背诵和觉悟的，有因此觉悟和接受劝告之人吗？</p>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "54:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>赛莫德人否认了他们使者撒立哈（愿主赐其平安）警告他们的，</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "54:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们谴责说：“我们怎能跟追随一个我们同类的凡人呢？假如我们就这样跟随他，那我们确是陷入错误和疯狂之中。</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "54:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>启示单降临给他一人，而我们大家没有吗？不然！这只是说谎者和自命不凡者。”</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "54:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在复活日，他们将知道谁是自命不凡的说谎者，谁是清廉者。是撒立哈，还是他们？</p>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "54:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我确从石头中取出那母驼，复活它以示对他们的考验。撒立哈啊！你当等待并观察他们将怎样对待那峰骆驼，以及那骆驼将怎样对待他们，你当坚忍他们的伤害。</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "54:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你告诉他们，他们井里的水是他们与母驼均分的，一日属于它，一日属于他们，在轮属的日子他们各自到井边来。</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "54:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们喊来自己的朋友，以便杀死那峰驼，那人就奉族人的命令拿起剑杀死了骆驼。</p>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "54:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>麦加的人们啊！你们想想我会怎样惩罚他们？我使给予他们的惩罚成为对世人的警告。</p>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "54:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我差遣一声呐喊毁灭了他们，他们便像羊圈栅栏所用树枝一般干枯。</p>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "54:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我确已使《古兰经》成为容易背诵和接受告诫的，有因此觉悟和接受劝告之人吗？</p>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "54:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>鲁特的民众否认了他们的使者鲁特（愿主赐他平安）警告他们的，</p>"
        },
        "34": {
            "verses": {
                "54:34": {
                    "id": 34
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我派出一股飓风，用石块袭击了他们，鲁特（愿主赐他平安）的家人没有遭遇惩罚，我拯救了他们免遭惩罚，他带着家人在惩罚来临前的夜里离开。</p>"
        },
        "35": {
            "verses": {
                "54:35": {
                    "id": 35
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我拯救他们免遭惩罚，那是我赐予他们的恩典，我以拯救鲁特的方式，报酬感谢真主恩惠之人。</p>"
        },
        "36": {
            "verses": {
                "54:36": {
                    "id": 36
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>鲁特曾以我的惩罚警告他们，而他们争论并否认了他。</p>"
        },
        "37": {
            "verses": {
                "54:37": {
                    "id": 37
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>鲁特的族人曾诱惑他，不要保护他天使的客人们，以便他们可以行丑事，故我遮蔽了他们的视觉，令他们无法看见天使，我对他们说：“尝试我的惩罚吧！那是我对你们的警告。”</p>"
        },
        "38": {
            "verses": {
                "54:38": {
                    "id": 38
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>一种恒久的惩罚在早晨来临他们，这惩罚一直跟随他们，直到后世这惩罚会再次降临。</p>"
        },
        "39": {
            "verses": {
                "54:39": {
                    "id": 39
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>有个声音对他们说：“你们尝试我为你们降下的惩罚吧！那是你们否认鲁特警告的结果。”</p>"
        },
        "40": {
            "verses": {
                "54:40": {
                    "id": 40
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我确已使《古兰经》成为容易背诵和接受告诫的，有因此觉悟和接受劝告之人吗？</p>"
        },
        "41": {
            "verses": {
                "54:41": {
                    "id": 41
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我的警告确已通过穆萨和哈伦（愿主赐他们平安）之口来临法老的民众，</p>"
        },
        "42": {
            "verses": {
                "54:42": {
                    "id": 42
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们否认了来自我的明证，故我以任何人都无法阻挡的严厉刑罚惩罚了他们，真主确是万能的。</p>"
        },
        "43": {
            "verses": {
                "54:43": {
                    "id": 43
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>麦加的人们啊！你们中不信道者比上述这些不信道者——奴哈的宗族、阿德人、赛莫德人、鲁特的族人、法老及他的民众——还优秀吗？难道你们拥有来自真主天经中的赦免吗？</p>"
        },
        "44": {
            "verses": {
                "54:44": {
                    "id": 44
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道麦加的这些不信道者说：“我们可以战胜任何欲伤害我们、破坏我们团结的人。”</p>"
        },
        "45": {
            "verses": {
                "54:45": {
                    "id": 45
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这些不信道者终将被战胜，在信士们面前他们败北，这在白德尔战役已经发生。</p>"
        },
        "46": {
            "verses": {
                "54:46": {
                    "id": 46
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们否认的复活就是他们被约定遭遇惩罚之时，复活日的惩罚比他们在白德尔遭遇更沉重、更严酷。</p>"
        },
        "47": {
            "verses": {
                "54:47": {
                    "id": 47
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>不信道和作恶的犯罪者，确是在远离真理的迷误和惩罚之中。</p>"
        },
        "48": {
            "verses": {
                "54:48": {
                    "id": 48
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们匍匐着被拖进火狱之日，有个声音怪责他们说：“你们品尝烈火的惩罚吧！”</p>"
        },
        "49": {
            "verses": {
                "54:49": {
                    "id": 49
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>宇宙间的万物都是依照我的知识、我所意欲的以及受保护的天牌上的记录，在预定中得以创造。</p>"
        },
        "50": {
            "verses": {
                "54:50": {
                    "id": 50
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当我欲一件事物时，我只要对那事物说“有”，霎时间，我所意欲的在片刻就有了。</p>"
        },
        "51": {
            "verses": {
                "54:51": {
                    "id": 51
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我毁灭的已逝民众中确有如同你们一样的不信道者，对此有觉悟故而远离不信道的人吗？</p>"
        },
        "52": {
            "verses": {
                "54:52": {
                    "id": 52
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>众仆的所有行为均被记录在功过簿中，任何事务都不会被遗漏。</p>"
        },
        "53": {
            "verses": {
                "54:53": {
                    "id": 53
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>一切大小行为和言语都记录在被保护的天牌中，众仆将依此得到报酬。</p>"
        },
        "54": {
            "verses": {
                "54:54": {
                    "id": 54
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>遵循真主命令、远离真主禁戒的敬畏者们，将进入下临诸河乐园。</p>"
        },
        "55": {
            "verses": {
                "54:55": {
                    "id": 55
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在掌握万物的主那里，他们将居住在一个真理的席位中，他们将于其中享受永恒的恩泽。</p>"
        }
    }
}